Computes reciprocal of square root of x element-wise.

@description

# Examples
```{r}
x <- k_convert_to_tensor(c(1, 10, 100))
k_rsqrt(x)
# array([1, 0.31622776, 0.1], dtype=float32)
```

@returns
A tensor with the same dtype as `x`.

@param x
input tensor

@export
@family math ops
@family ops
